Title: What Power is...
Plot: Aceveda finds himself in a near fatal confrontation, and enlists Vic to help him take down the suspects in order to help service his own personal agenda.  Meanwhile after losing her position of power, Claudette rejoins Dutch on the search for the cuddler rapist as they get a stunning break in the case.
GuestStars: Clark Gregg, David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Michele Hicks, DeLane Matthews, Monnae Michaell, Rebecca Pidgeon, Camillia Sanes, Larry Sullivan, Rif Hutton, Kurt Caceres, Wilmer Calderon
